111source rpm package
take the rpm source package "build-2011.03.29-6.1.src.rpm" for example;
1 rpm -ivh package name;
    rpm -ivh build-2011.03.29-6.1.src.rpm
 
 then the sourc file and spec file will be found in /root/rebuild/

2 we can rebuild the rpm package via building spec file;the spec file is just a script file for rpm rebuilding;
    the command is :
    rpmbuild --ba build.spec

then the rpm file will be generated in /root/rebuild/RPMS directory;

3 and the following things is just install the general rpm package;
